2026-05-16T02:35:58.0339516Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0340340Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0341508Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0342369Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0343227Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0344130Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
