2026-05-16T02:35:58.0347156Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0347902Z 22    <!--
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0378990Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0379756Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0380410Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0381236Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0382025Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0382859Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0383630Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0384402Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0385145Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0385848Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0386386Z 33    -->
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0386947Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0387906Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-16T02:35:58.0389039Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
