2026-05-16T02:35:58.1053309Z 258            triggers an IllegalArgumentException ("List adapter activity
2026-05-16T02:35:58.1054321Z 259            trampoline invoked without specifying target intent"). Adding
2026-05-16T02:35:58.1055038Z 260            excludeFromRecents removes the Recents restoration vector,
