2026-05-16T02:35:58.6180169Z 12    <!--
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6180519Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6180854Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6181860Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6182219Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6182631Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
