2026-05-16T02:35:58.6411288Z 249            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6411633Z 250            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6411966Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6412316Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6412543Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6412925Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6413271Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T02:35:58.6413589Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
